Indien u van adres verander het, of Indle en besonderhede vanu huidige adres, by. straathaam ervol -rommer, ens. verander het, KUNENE moet die vom KENNISGEWING VAN ADRESVERANDERI ING. wat In die sakkle agter in die identiten tsdokument ls, gebruik word om die verandering aar temeld enmoet dit ingedien word by of gepos word aan die naaste streek distrikkantoon yan die DEPARTEMENT VAN BINNELANDSE. SAKE RICHARD GEBOORTEOISTRIK OF-LAND/ DISTRICT OR COUNTRY OF BIRTH SOUTH AFRICA REGISTERED RES DENTIAL AND POSTAL ADDRESS GEBOORTEGATUM 1: Keep the proof of your REGISTERED RESIDENTIAL AND DATE OF, BIRTH 1962-06-13 POSTAL ADDRESS in this pocket, DATUM UITGEREIK 2. If you have changed your eddress, or, if particulars of your DATE ISSUED present address, e.g. name of street and/or street number, atc., have been changed, the NOTICE OF CHANGE OF ADDRESS form in the 1997-02-28 packet at the back of the identity document must be used to report the change and it must be handed in at or posted to the nearest 01 OP GESAS NAN DE DIREKTEUR GENERAAL regional'district office of the DEPARTMENT OF HOME AFFAIRS. BINNELANDSE SAKH BY AUTHORITY DP THE PARECTOR GENERAL HOHE AFFAIRS
